text: Novofyodorovskoye () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Ashkadarsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 328 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 28 km from Sterlitamak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Novofyodorovskoye (rural locality)
